items.typeLine: Guardian's Corvine Charm of the Guardian
explicitMods: Grants Armour equal to 5% of your Reserved Mana to you and nearby Allies
If you've Attacked Recently, you and nearby Allies have +8% Chance to Block Attack Damage
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Charm Socket on the Wildwood Primalist Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.

items.name: Split Personality

This Jewel's Socket has 25% increased effect per Allocated Passive Skill between
it and your Class' starting location
+40 to Evasion Rating
+5 to maximum Mana
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: You need not go looking for a second opinion.

items.name: Watcher's Eye
explicitMods: 5% increased maximum Energy Shield
6% increased maximum Life
4% increased maximum Mana
30% increased Maximum total Energy Shield Recovery per second from Leech while affected by Zealotry
Non-Channelling Skills have -7 to Total Mana Cost while affected by Clarity
Unaffected by Vulnerability while affected by Determination
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: One by one, they stood their ground against a creature
they had no hope of understanding, let alone defeating,
and one by one, they became a part of it.
